{
  "stem": "5225.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because you see, we didn't use light.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To work, we only used daylight, the daylight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We wake up [INAUDIBLE] in the summer, at 6:00.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you work until 6:00, 7:30 in the night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we didn't even go to-- for-- supper was in the middle of the day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was not such as-- like here you go for supper out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Supper-- and she brought the machine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The girl brought the machine the food-- potatoes, with a borscht, with [NON-ENGLISH]-- hamburgers, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You eat.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You finish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You start work again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because the time was-- catch the light.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because we don't work-- in this time was I think you supposed to pay for 1 kilowatt four, four hours work, for one kilowatt.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Was so high, the electricity, that we mostly didn't use electricity in, in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we do the best what we can.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that's it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the holidays.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All holidays.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, in our house really was a small-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A small-- not a synagogue, a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A shtiebel.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they call it [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, when you're poor a girl, and if you cannot get married because of money, this, this one helped you out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And only Friday they can get-- you can get married for them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they give you 25 zlotlys, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they prepare, give you a supper on Friday night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's what you get.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But never-- they say never a Jew-- a Jewish wedding will fall apart because of money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So this was their slogan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we was going.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a shul.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I remember when I was 16 years old, I was singing by a Hazzan He was the biggest in Poland, in Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
